reviewText: LOVE the movies Class and Making the Grade- two of my favorite 80s flicks in one box! 80s fans with love the pure hilarious ridicilousness of these two movies. :D Decided to give Johnny be Good a chance, and it's truly one of the worst movies I've ever seen in life. Not even hilariously bad- just bad! That's why I gave this disc 4 stars instead of 5.
Making the grade is great 80's movie before american pie
